init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans were able to use their magic to create weapons, and armor, and even to create a shield around the Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans were able to destroy the alien ships and they were able to drive them away from Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shield was created from the human's own magic, and it was powered by the mana of the humans.
